title: Emerica x Skateline NBD Collab Featuring Gary Rogers
description:
Emerica x Skateline NBD Collab: http://emerica.com/shoes/herman-g6-vulc-x-skateline/black/

Emerica is proud to announce the release of our newest collab, the Skateline NBD x Herman G6 Vulc, bringing Gary Rogers into the mix front and center, backing his favorite brand, Emerica.
 
With Gary hosting the most popular skate show on the planet, Skateline, it only made sense to , well, let Gary be Gary.  And that’s exactly what he did.
